thread.title: Protolabs Sets Conference Call to Discuss First Quarter 2018 Financial Results

author: cnbc.com
title: Protolabs Sets Conference Call to Discuss First Quarter 2018 Financial Results
text:
MAPLE PLAIN, Minn.--(BUSINESS WIRE)-- Protolabs (NYSE: PRLB) announced today that it will issue its financial results for the first quarter 2018 before the opening of the market on Apr. 26, 2018. Protolabs will host a call to discuss the results at 8:30 a.m. Eastern time on the same day. A simultaneous webcast of the call will be available via the investor relations section of the Protolabs website and the following link: https://edge.media-server.com/m6/p/obx9hij8
To access the live call, please dial 877-709-8150 or outside the U.S. dial 201-689-8354 at least five minutes prior to the 8:30 a.m. start time. An audio replay will be available at the investor relations section of the Protolabs website beginning approximately two hours following the end of the conference call.
